        {
            "+content": "Akihito is a college student obsessed with good looks and carnal pleasure, but he can't stand the handsome-yet-aloof Sae. Things come to a head when Akihito is shot down at a singles mixer by a girl who has set her romantic sights on Sae. Furious, he follows Sae to the hotel district, where he learns Sae's secret: he's gay, and he's having trouble enjoying himself in the bedroom. Breaking through Sae's mental barriers is exactly the sexy challenge Akihito needed. <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
